{"tid":1467867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（必睇） 集中討論今次機場補救措施","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:15.000Z","uid":172129,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a85089017166b4a86b75ae61eed998083be7be56","tid":1467867,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"作為和理非，對今次機場事件係有少許失望，但我好相信可以逸回劣勢，首先有唔好再互相指責，最重要係做補救措施<br />\n<br />\n我建議，如下<br />\n<br />\n1: 舉牌向受影響旅客表達因靜坐而有任何影響表達「sorry」 <br />\n<br />\n2: 主動上前協助受影響旅客，以禮貌態度問及答，可參考<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1464417/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1464417/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（緊記： 入到機場後，全世界都係以放大鏡望緊我地，幫受影響既旅客係會加分）<br />\n<br />\n3: 務必遵守軍規<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465135/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465135/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n各位仲有建議既可以提議下"},{"pid":"4a8392aa686005929360a0efe85c626bbb307677","tid":1467867,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊整小册子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8ac2e15613eb0402fd22003a4e29afafd72763f","tid":1467867,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"113f91d534a44386d438100ba103a9aea7c6089b","tid":1467867,"uid":35364,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"捉到對家又唔想失威，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷就足夠，<br />\n手持「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類。<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其<strong>象徵意義</strong>。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。"},{"pid":"3b46add3a95ddd7d6326e78ca061d126f1f6f658","tid":1467867,"uid":172129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi